title: Virtual_Villagers_1-5_Including_Walkthroughs(TigaHotty85)
description:
I downloaded this from PirateBay from someone else. I did not crack them myself. I just decided to search the net and get ahold of the "Walkthroughs" for each game. 

Reason is when I downloaded this I did so from another PC because my internet was down at the time. After putting it to my computer I started from game 1 and started to play. But when I got stuck I had no way to look up any help so I was very frustrated and had to stop playing because I could go no further.

I did this so others who want to download these games have access to the walkthrough's "Offline" with no worries about getting stuck.

Hope I helped!

Please seed!

Thanks!
